      <h1 class='title'>Remand Prisoners</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 c124WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_124ws' title='Col. 124WS &mdash; HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 c124WS' name='column_124ws' href='#column_124ws' rel='bookmark'>124WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-05401'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_646'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-simon-hughes' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_646' title='Link to this speech by Mr Simon Hughes' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-simon-hughes" title="Mr Simon Hughes">Simon Hughes</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-05401">To ask the Secretary of State for the Home Department pursuant to his answer of <a href="/written_answers/2003/jun/23/prison-drug-rehabilitation-programmes#column_603w">23 June 2003,<span class="italic">Official Report</span>, column 603W</a>, on remand prisoners, (1) how many <span class="italic">(a)</span> unconvicted and <span class="italic">(b)</span> convicted unsentenced prisoners have been held in prison for more than 24 months in each of the last five years; [131768]</p><p id="S6CV0412P0-05402">(2) what assessment he has made of the reasons for the recent change in the number of prisoners held on remand for more than 24 months. [131651]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-05403'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_647'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-paul-goggins' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_647' title='Link to this speech by Mr Paul Goggins' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-paul-goggins" title="Mr Paul Goggins">Paul Goggins</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-05403">I refer the hon. Member to my letter of 16 October 2003.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
